two delinquent young lovers from the suburbs of Los Angeles, traveling to a small
Texas town to falsely claim a dead friend's inheritance. The two teens, haunted
by their own dubious pasts while pursuing their scam, wind up in a nightmare of
greed and betrayal when confronted with the twisted and bizarre underworld of
Tremo, TX - population 2870.
